* &quot;Détruire, dit-elle&quot; (Les Éditions de Minuit, 1969). &quot;Destroy, She Said&quot;, trans. Barbara Bray (1970)
* &quot;Abahn Sabana David&quot; (Gallimard, 1970). &quot;Abahn Sabana David&quot;, trans. Kazim Ali (2016)
*&quot; Ah! Ernesto&quot; (Hatlin Quist, 1971)
